command.name: help

php /home/vaishnavmhetre/Workplace/job_evaluation/hospitalsearch/artisan help list

You can also output the help in other formats by using the --format option:

command.name: list
command.help:
The list command lists all commands:

php /home/vaishnavmhetre/Workplace/job_evaluation/hospitalsearch/artisan list

You can also display the commands for a specific namespace:

php /home/vaishnavmhetre/Workplace/job_evaluation/hospitalsearch/artisan list test

You can also output the information in other formats by using the --format option:

php /home/vaishnavmhetre/Workplace/job_evaluation/hospitalsearch/artisan list --format=xml

It's also possible to get raw list of commands (useful for embedding command runner):

php /home/vaishnavmhetre/Workplace/job_evaluation/hospitalsearch/artisan list --raw

--formatThe output format (txt, xml, json, or md)
